---
title: Craveworthy Caprese Sandwich Serves 1 | with Balsamic-Tomato Salad
description: A grab-and-go sandwich, full of summer salad flavours! Rich basil pesto, creamy bocconcini and sweet tomatoes make a tasty trio in this easy sandwich.
